IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DATA-E2E.

DATA DIVISION.
01 COUNTER          PICTURE IS 9(5).
01 MESSAGE          PICTURE IS X(20).
01 SALARY           PICTURE IS 9(7)V99.
01 FLAG             PICTURE IS A.
01 ARRAY-ITEMS      PICTURE IS 9(3) OCCURS 5 TIMES.
01 EMPLOYEE.
   05 EMP-NAME      PICTURE IS X(30).
   05 EMP-ID        PICTURE IS 9(5).
01 TOTAL            PICTURE IS 9(10).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "DATA E2E START"

    MOVE 1000 TO COUNTER
    DISPLAY "COUNTER: " COUNTER

    MOVE "HELLO DATA DIVISION" TO MESSAGE
    DISPLAY "MESSAGE: " MESSAGE

    MOVE 50000.99 TO SALARY
    DISPLAY "SALARY: " SALARY

    MOVE "A" TO FLAG
    DISPLAY "FLAG: " FLAG

    MOVE 10 TO ARRAY-ITEMS
    DISPLAY "ARR-SLOT1: " ARRAY-ITEMS

    MOVE "JOHN DOE" TO EMP-NAME
    MOVE 42 TO EMP-ID
    DISPLAY "EMP-NAME: " EMP-NAME
    DISPLAY "EMP-ID: " EMP-ID

    ADD 500 TO COUNTER GIVING TOTAL
    DISPLAY "TOTAL: " TOTAL

    DISPLAY "DATA E2E END"


